22.  The expected outputs will be  
(i)  a report on the review of current literature and projects on the use of remote 
sensing and similar technology for agricultural and rural statistics; 
(ii)  reports on the seminars, training, and conferences; 
(iii)  reports on coordination issues, as needed; 
(iv)  draft technical reports and handbook; and 
(v)  monthly reports on the progress of the project in the Lao PDR, Philippines, 
Thailand, and Viet Nam.
